{"word":"ποδώκης","slug":"ποδώκης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ποδώκης</b></el> <el>(ποδ-ώκης, ες) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὠκύς'><el>ὠκύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>swiftfooted</i>, of Achilles, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>π. ἄνθρωπος</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>λαγώς</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>swift, quick</i>, <el>ὄμμα</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; <el>θεῶν π. βλάβαι</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}